{"tid":758534,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔知wow左未] 港蝗教你平食日本大學canteen","createTime":"2018-07-27T18:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T04:53:10.000Z","uid":12618,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c2a2c1ba2fd350bb276bb03add39dfef9437dd6e","tid":758534,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T18:57:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mofaalan/videos/10217142901952484/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmofaalan%2Fvideos%2F10217142901952484%2F&d=vfnmRlrYv4aOc28zMSbggtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=1e062b5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mofaalan/videos/10217142901952484/</a><br />\n<br />\n睇個嘴臉已經知係貪小便宜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個老母啲眼神幾凌厲<br />\n個老豆個樣係幾咁柒<br />\n個小朋友係咁既環境長大可想而知佢係會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你都攞左舊錢出黎比機票酒店<br />\n點解唔可以攞多舊錢出黎for飲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無錢唔好去旅行<br />\n失禮自己更失禮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01171ad3b5a566a6fa2146e48e2ab1ec681137f1","tid":758534,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T19:02:30.000Z","msg":"原post已del"},{"pid":"e5f57edc5e7a390e0bfc3fe09f028a1df39afb04","tid":758534,"uid":117042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T19:17:37.000Z","msg":"拿！有人直接去佢page鬧，page admin全部刪曬，又冇出post道歉，既然咁冇反省之意，我會揾成日鬧蝗蟲嘅日本人開post同大仁生活開拖！"},{"pid":"52cf87330eee97dbcd2d1208d24fc430d3074604","tid":758534,"uid":146917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T19:25:27.000Z","msg":"想平去貧民窟啦"},{"pid":"4e17f167591f7271e752b9c77ec4a95877c2a285","tid":758534,"uid":117042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T19:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/033628_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0